      • onInputPartSearch

        public void onInputPartSearch​(javafx.scene.input.KeyEvent keyEvent)
        check if query is numerical, and lookupPart for ID. If query is not numerical, an exception will be thrown from parseInt and caught. in case of exception, lookupPart will be called with a string instead.
